<h2>⚠️ Security Scan: Issues Found</h2>

<div class="alert-warning">
    <strong>{{scan_type}} scan found {{issues_count}} issues in {{repo_name}}</strong>
</div>

<div class="stats-grid">
    <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">{{repo_name}}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Repository</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">{{issues_count}}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Issues Found</div>
    </div>
</div>

<p>Please review the scan results and address any security vulnerabilities.</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    <a href="{{app_url}}/admin/repos" class="button">View Scan Results</a>
</p>